      • select

        public static String select(String select,
                            List<String> groups)
        Parse a select string, and merge it with a match groups vector to produce an output string. Each group placeholder in the select string is replaced with the group at the corresponding index in the match groups vector
        Parameters:
        select - The select string
        groups - The match groups
        Returns:
        The output string with the merged selection
